{"name":"Accurate Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an accurate attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on the effect modifier of the attack and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"ztt7sio66u"}
{"name":"Agile Feint","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use your Acrobatics bonus or movement speed rank in place of Deception to feint and trick in combat.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"mibjuwdmw5m"}
{"name":"All-out Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an all-out attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on your active defenses (Dodge and Parry) and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"turtc0tiyol"}
{"name":"Animal Empathy","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have a special connection with animals. You can use interaction skills on animals normally, and do not have to speak a language the animal understands.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"egzh5je9kjc"}
{"name":"Artificer","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use the Expertise: Magic skill to create temporary magical devices.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"5m0mm06be6d"}
{"name":"Assessment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use Insight to able to judge an opponent’s relative combat capabilities.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"yqrpmlutfhe"}
{"name":"Attractive","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You are particularly attractive, giving you a +2 circumstance bonus on Deception and Persuasion checks to deceive, mislead, or influence others who are attracted to you. Rank 2 gives a +5 bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"rmin4psf8p"}
{"name":"Beginner's Luck","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>By spending a hero point, you gain an effective 5 ranks in a skill in which you currently have 0 ranks.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"gb2bdn9lbo7"}
{"name":"Benefit","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have some significant social or structural benefit, such as wealth, status, or a secret identity. Each rank provides one benefit.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"6oa5y3djjgn"}
{"name":"Chokehold","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you successfully grab and maintain a hold on an opponent, you can suffocate them.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"y9jtni4cut"}
{"name":"Connected","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You know people who can help you out. You can call in favors by making a Persuasion check.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"0fvysrcq6y2f"}
{"name":"Contacts","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have extensive contacts. You can make an Investigation check to gather information in only one minute.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"7lv99xweuyl"}
{"name":"Daze","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can make a Deception or Intimidation check as a standard action to cause an opponent to hesitate in combat.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":2,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"han5ligqhkq"}
{"name":"Defensive Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Trade up to -5 attack bonus for an equal bonus (+5) to active defenses.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"ijwjutrol2l"}
{"name":"Defensive Roll","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Receive a bonus to Toughness equal to rank. This is an active defense and is lost if vulnerable or defenseless.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"eadtt8k09qr"}
{"name":"Diehard","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Automatically stabilize on the round after your condition becomes dying.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"q0wxl7zt1d"}
{"name":"Eidetic Memory","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Perfect recall. +5 circumstance bonus on memory checks. Can make Expertise checks as if trained.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"eue6vp95nbw"}
{"name":"Equipment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have 5 points per rank to spend on equipment, vehicles, and headquarters.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"w2gqr73nx0r"}
{"name":"Evasion","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus to Dodge checks to avoid area effects. Rank 2 increases bonus to +5.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":2,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"v3s4vnva9"}
{"name":"Extraordinary Effort","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Gain two benefits of extra effort at once, but you become exhausted on the following turn.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"0mu8u19vir4"}
{"name":"Fascinate","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>One interaction skill captures attention. Target is entranced if check succeeds.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"i78mngv50n"}
{"name":"Fast Grab","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Make a free grab check after hitting with an unarmed attack.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"swzghrw2lnl"}
{"name":"Favored Environment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus to attack or active defense in a specific environment.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"1rhs272e9p3"}
{"name":"Favored Foe","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus on interaction and perception checks against a particular type of opponent.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"hhinqdpl8x"}
{"name":"Fearless","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You are immune to fear effects.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"2rt5671gjwa"}
{"name":"Grabbing Finesse","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Use Dexterity bonus instead of Strength bonus to make grab attacks.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"dinr6d8r6b"}
{"name":"Great Endurance","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+5 bonus on checks to avoid fatigue and to hold your breath.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"tzmkg9aq5"}